    {
      id: "0200000000800000",
      title: "Long distance relations",
      x: 9,
      y: 0,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "0300000000800000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:quantum_entangloporter",
          count: 2
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Quantum Entangloporters are for your long-range transport of either items, power, fluids or gasses (Heat seems to be non-functional in Mekanism 9.2).", "To get started with it, place it down and assign it either a public or private channel (pipes wont connect otherwise).", "This QE has all the Side Configs available, and everything (including Energy) has Auto-push set to Off, so make sure to set all of them to On, if it's your output QE.", "The stats of the QE is (as per Mekanism 9.2, MC1.10.2):", "1 item per second", "6.4 Million RF/t", "256 mb/t gas/fluid.", "This limit is per channel, so you can't have 2 pairs of QEs to transfer 800k RF/t on the same channel. You can still have 2 pairs of QEs on 2 different channels to transfer 800k RF/t."],
      icon: "mekanism:quantum_entangloporter",
      dependencies: ["02000000007F0000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "0400000000800000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:alloy_atomic",
          count: 8,
