        {
          id: "0300000000810002",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:chemical_crystallizer"
        }
      ],
      description: ["The final stage of Mekanism Ore Processing, and overall it's going to be a big setup. The Quintuple Ore Processing adds 3 steps of processing the ores, and 4 steps of gas production.", "The gas production is covered in the linked quests.", "For the ore processing, it goes through the Chemical Dissolution Chamber, where Sulfuric Acid (left gas input) and ores (top item input) are added.", "Then outputs (right gas output) to the Chemical Washer where Water is added (top fluid input)", "Then outputs (right gas output) to the Chemical Crystalizer (right item output).", "After the Crystalizer, it has to go through the Quadruple Ore Processing and down.", "NOTE: You may want a x5 set for every processable ore (7 different ores in 9.2.2), as it may not use all the fluids when fully upgraded."],
      icon: "mekanism:chemical_dissolution_chamber",
      dependencies: ["02000000007F0000", "0200000000820000"],
