      tasks: [
        {
          id: "0300000000860000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:rotary_condensentrator"
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Rotary Condensentrator (RC) can turn Liquid into Gas, and vice versa.", "The RC is side specific for Gas/Liquid in/output.", "The small (left when placed in front) connection is for Gas, the big (right when placed in front) connection is for Liquid. You can also just see if the cable connects or not.", "In the GUI you can switch its conversion function. Condensentrating for Gas to Liquid, and De-Condensentrating for Liquid to Gas.", "There is no Auto-Eject with the RC, so to pull from it, you will have to use the Configurator to set your output pipe to PULL."],
      icon: "mekanism:rotary_condensentrator",
