      ],
      description: ["Multiblock structure that allows you to teleport between Teleporter setups.", "The structure is a Teleporter at the bottom middle, with a 3x1x4 frame. The Teleporter does require power to function, but uses very little per teleport.", "To set up the teleporters, you need to set it to a Frequency (or make one), and then set the other end to the same Frequency to link them.", "More than 2 Teleporters linked to the same Frequency can be wonky, so you might want to have an Entrance and an Exit portal at each location (if you have more than 2 locations)"],
      icon: "mekanism:teleporter",
