    {
      id: "0200000000890000",
      title: "The Ignition",
      x: 9,
      y: 10,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "0300000000890000",
          type: "checkmark",
          title: "checkbox"
        }
      ],
      description: ["To start the Fusion Reactor itself, there are serveral things that needs to be in order.", "Almost all of these are covered by quests, the rest are here.", "You need enough RF stored in the Laser Amplifier (~800mil RF or more).", "You need to produce Deterium and Tritium as fuel for the Reactor.", "You need a Hohlraum with D-T Fuel in the Controller.", "The next step, is to go into the Controller, go to Fuel and set the Injection Rate to 2.", "After that, you activate the Laser Amplifier (by setting redstone mode from \"High\" to \"Low\", or giving it a redstone signal) to shoot into the Laser Matrix Focus, which should cause the ignition.", "If it didn't, you have to store up RF again and possibly place a new Hohlraum in the Controller."],
      icon: "mekanism:laser_amplifier",
      dependencies: ["02000000008A0000"],
      rewards: [
