      ],
      description: ["This is the ultimate Reactor for Mekanism, that has a minimum generation of 200.000 rf/t.", "It's quite complicated to get starting, so the explanation will be split between the connected quests of the Fusion Reactor.", "This quest will explain the structure of the Fusion Reactor.", "The base is going to be a 3x3 of Reactor Casing, with 1 additional Casing at N, S, E and W (13 blocks total).", "The 2nd layer will form a 5x5 square without corners on top (12 blocks total).", "The 3rd layer will a 5x5 square With corners. One of the middle blocks has to be the Laser Focus Matrix, side doesn't matter (16 blocks total).", "The 4th layer is exactly like the 2nd (12 blocks total).", "The 5th layer is like the first layer, except the Reactor Controller needs to be in the middle (13 blocks total).", "If the structure is correct, the Controller will light up.", "On each side, the middle 5 blocks (shaped like a +, or in other words, all the edge blocks needs to be Reactor Casing) can be exchanged for either Reactor Glass (to look inside), or Reactor Ports. You will need at least 3 Reactor Ports in total. 2 for Fuel Input, 1 for Power Output.", "The only blocks that can't be replaced for Reactor Glass or Reactor Ports is the Controller and Laser Focus Matrix that needs a central spot."],
      icon: "mekanismgenerators:reactor_glass",
      dependencies: ["02000000007F0000", "0200000000990000", "02000000009A0000"],
