      description: ["Things are starting to heat up.", "Fuelwood Heater creates heat by burning fuel, and Resistive Heater converts Energy into Heat.", "Heat can be transfered with Thermodynamic Conductors.", "Heat can be applied to the Thermoelectric Boiler, and the Thermal Evaporation Plant (requires Vavle input)"],
