      ],
      description: ["Sulfur can be hard to get your hands on from mining. Luckily there are ways to produce it all the way from Cobblestone (which is pretty easy to get your hands on).", "This is a 4 machine setup.", "Cobblestone goes into a Crusher, which outputs Gravel.", "Gravel goes a Purification Chamber with Oxygen to produce 1:1 Flint.", "Flint goes into a Crusher to make it into Gunpowder.", "Gunpowder goes into a Chemical Injection Chamber with Hydrogen Chloride to output Sulfur Dust.", "The Sulfur Dust then goes into the Chemical Oxydizer for the Quintuple Ore Processing."],
