    {
      id: "02000000008F0000",
      title: "Next Level Tool",
      x: 10,
      y: 0,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "03000000008F0000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:atomic_disassembler"
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Atomic Disassembler is the ultimate all-in-one tool, so it counts as Pickaxe, Axe, Shovel, Hoe and Sword (20 hearts). It uses RF instead of durability, but each broken block/attack uses RF.", "If it runs out of RF, it will mine slower than a Wooden Pickaxe, its Vein mode ceases to work and only does 4 hearts.", "It has 5 modes, that can be switched between by Shift Right-Clicking. Fast, Normal, Slow, Vein, Off.", "Fast Mode is the same speed as a Diamond Pick with Efficiency V and Haste II.", "Normal Mode is like a Diamond Pick, with Efficiency V", "Slow Mode is like a Diamond Pick, unenchanted.", "The Vein mode, takes all the blocks of that type touching the one you mined - Only works on Ores and Wood Logs. It can not be used to clear out Stone and the like.", "The Off mode, disables all its tool abilities, making it unable to break blocks, and turns it into a Sword.", "The Atomic Disassembler tills dirt AND grass in a 1x1 on Slow/Off, 3x3 on Normal/Vein and 5x5 on Fast. It can not make Grass Paths.", "The Atomic Disassembler can not be enchanted."],
      icon: "mekanism:atomic_disassembler",
      dependencies: ["02000000007F0000"],
