          id: "0300000000930000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:hdpe_sheet",
          count: 16
        }
      ],
      description: ["Plastic blocks are aesthetic blocks with a Very flat color.", "You are going to need another Pressurized Reaction Chamber for its second function, Oxygen, Substrate and Liquid Ethylene which we covered the last couple of quests.", "The Substrate will turn into HDPE Pellets. which can be turned into HDPE Sheets, which can be turned into Plastic Blocks.", "Making HDPE Pellets will give Oxygen as a side product, which can be reused. It just has to be piped out and back in.", "A note to make, is that a Biofuel -> Substrate will create more Ethylene than a Substrate -> HDPE Pellet requires, so you will have leftover, which you can use in a Gas-Burning Generator."],
      icon: "mekanism:hdpe_sheet",
      dependencies: ["02000000007C0000", "0200000000860000"],
