          type: "item",
          item: "mekanismgenerators:hohlraum"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Before the Reactor can start up and produce power, it needs a kickstart injection of D-T Fuel, which is done through the Hohlraum with D-T Fuel in it.", "To get D-T Fuel into it, place it in the [+], in either the Chemical Infuser or a Gas Tank with D-T Fuel."],
