          id: "0300000000960001",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:rotary_condensentrator"
        }
      ],
      description: ["When you have your Liquid Lithium, you have to convert it into gas with the Rotary Condensentrator, and then transfer the Lithium gas into a Solar Neutron Activator to get Tritium.", "The Solar Neutron Activator does require HDPE Sheets to make, so you should probably look into the Plastic quest if you haven't done so yet.", "The Solar Neutron Activate takes IN gas from the Bottom, and outputs at the front.", "The Solar Neutron Activator needs Sunlight to process the Lithium. Transparent blocks like glass can be put above it.", "Tritium should be pumped directly into the Reactor."],
