          type: "item",
          item: "mekanismgenerators:gas_burning_generator"
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Gas-Burning Generators does as the name implies, generate power from burning gas.", "It can burn Hydrogen and Ethylene for power generation only.", "Burning Hydrogen gives you no power gain at all in Mekanism V9, and will give you exactly the same amount of power back, that you used to create that Hydrogen.", "Burning Ethylene though, is very much worth it, and a really good mid-game source of power, given you have plenty of materials to turn into Bio Fuel"],
