      ],
      description: ["[This quest chain focuses on power production]", "Pressurized Reaction Chamber is used to create Ethylene, Substrate and HDPE Pellets from Biofuel.", "Its first function is creating Substrate from Biofuel, Hydrogen and Water, with Ethylene (gas) as a side product.", "You may want to configure the in/output sides on the PRC.", "The Ethylene is going to be used in the following quest.", "The Substrate is going to be a waste product here."],
