          count: 4
        },
        {
          id: "03000000009D0003",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:pressure_disperser",
          count: 4
        }
      ],
      description: ["The Thermoelectric Boiler multistructure that creates Steam from Water and Heat.", "The structure requirements is seen in the Crafting Task. The minimum size for a Boiler is 3x3x4, but with the crafting and reward, there is exactly enough for a 4x4x9.", "The base and edges has to be Boiler Casing. The walls has to be Boiler Casing, Boiler Valve or Structural Glass.", "The inside of the Boiler is split into 2 parts: Water storage (Bottom part) and Steam storage (Upper part). The Water storage is where the Superheating Elements will go. They don't have be in any particular shape, aslong as they are connected. The more Superheating Elements you have, the faster it can produce Steam.", "The top part has to be separated with Pressure Dispersers (full layer), which is where the steam is stored and extracted. The Water input Valve, has to be below the Pressure Dispersers, while the Steam output has to be on level or above the Pressure Dispersers (while still on the wall)"],
      icon: "mekanism:superheating_element",
      dependencies: ["02000000008B0000"],
      rewards: [
        {
          id: "04000000009D0000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:structural_glass",
          count: 54
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      id: "02000000009E0000",
      title: "My Final Factory!",
      x: 15,
      y: 0,
      tasks: [
        {
          id: "03000000009E0000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:elite_smelting_factory"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Elite Factories are the last step.", "They have 7 Processing Slots, and like the rest, they use energy based on the amount of operations running.Elite is the last tier of Factories.", "Like the previous Factory quests, crafting any Elite Factory will do, despite the Crafting Task saying \"Elite Smeling Factory\".", "Note: The Ultimate Tier Installer can only be used on Fluid and Gas tanks."],
      icon: "mekanism:elite_smelting_factory",
      dependencies: ["02000000007F0000"],
      rewards: [
