          id: "0300000000A40000",
          type: "item",
          item: "mekanism:chemical_infuser"
        }
      ],
      description: ["Chemical Infuser infuses 2 gasses together to create a 3rd one.", "Inputs are on the sides (Chemical Infuser has no side specific inputs for any recipe), output is in the front.", "To make Hydrogen Chloride, you need Hydrogen from an Electrolytical Separator with Water, and Chloride from an Eletrolytical Separator with Brine.", "", "NOTE: Putting Brine in a Eletrolytical Separator will also produce Sodium, which currently has no use, so don't worry about storing it."],
