  subtitle: ["This is Part 2 of Mekanism.", "This is where things starts to take a step up in complexity, which means that there will be no more \"funny/silly\" descriptions, and focus mainly on the explanation of the machines.", "Part 2 includes The Elite and The Ultimate parts of Mekanism.", "", "Authored by Discomanco."],
